##############INSTALLATION/RUNNING/SETUP GUIDE#################

Simple execution

Step 1:
	Change directory to src folder
	cd yourpathname/src
Step 2:
	Start the server using
	python3 server.py
	Enter total number of questions and hit Y to accept clients
Step 3:
	Server waits until client is started
	Client is started by this process
	python3 client.py
	Enter name and automatically connect to server
Step 4:
	Repeat step 3 after wanting to accept more clients
Step 5:
	Communicate between server and client
Step 6:
	Communication ends and final result is displayed
